get.com/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-review-specs-price-photo-and-video-take-center-stage-140034341.html">89 分的评分</a>，目前是我们<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-smartphones-140004900.html">智能手机购买指南</a>中 Android 手机的首选。它几乎具备您对高端手持设备所期望的一切：华丽的 6.8 英寸 OLED 显示屏，具有 120Hz 的快速刷新率、灵活的 Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 处理器、一流的制造质量、超过一整天的电池生活和强大的摄像系统。它配备了 S Pen 手写笔，三星将为该设备提供五年的安全补丁和四年的操作系统更新。您可能需要付出一些额外的工作才能释放这些相机的全部潜力，而且三星的软件仍然有些臃肿，但 S23 Ultra 绝对是一款优质设备。最大的打击是价格昂贵，但这笔交易对此有所帮助。</p><h2>三星 Galaxy S23 </h2><p><core-commerce id="a12311001eb14b60b2471a32714e4fa1" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>基本款<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJMUDJQWTZOP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFwaC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNzk4MjUwYTYtZTNmOS00OWU4LTkzYzYtYjhhZGQ4YzY0MWVhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAS1ZgdMVGeFoqzpRVobt2hGN56PFQtzsfm9Jn8V7MWEt&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BLP2PY6N" class="rapid-with-clickid">Galaxy S23</a> 128GB 型号售价降至 600 美元， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJMUDNaTVpQP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFwaC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNzk4MjUwYTYtZTNmOS00OWU4LTkzYzYtYjhhZGQ4YzY0MWVhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAARbkdAyhYej8r3miDdJ-ILpw0-X93WjsfSXMqehC9tjV&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BLP3ZMZP" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BLP3ZMZP?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">256GB 型号</a>售价降至 660 美元。这两项交易均提供约 140 美元的折扣，与我们追踪的最低价格相符。 Galaxy S23 在电池续航时间、相机硬件和充电速度方面落后于 S23 Ultra，但这仍然为一款快速、充满活力的设备留下了空间，该设备将在未来几年内获得更新。除了成本较低之外，考虑它的最大原因是它是市场上最小的高端手机之一，拥有 6.1 英寸的显示屏，应该可以让很多人用一只手轻松使用。</p><h2>三星 Galaxy S23+ </h2><p><core-commerce id="30a7786ebcd64527bf42819cd95a6cdb" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> 256GB <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJMUDRKOVJSP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFwaC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNzk4MjUwYTYtZTNmOS00OWU4LTkzYzYtYjhhZGQ4YzY0MWVhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAXpfJlQmLAbv_ML3-r_TnKye4P8smeROIl3YPaXy3xnD&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BLP4J9RR" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BLP4J9RR?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">三星 Galaxy S23+ 的</a>售价为 750 美元，这是解锁型号的又一个历史最低价，比该型号的典型售价低约 150 美元。 <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJMUDNLMjhTP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFwaC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNzk4MjUwYTYtZTNmOS00OWU4LTkzYzYtYjhhZGQ4YzY0MWVhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAVoOmpea7zi-wfPchVWZZk7MrQC-3iWoQONalICXms1-&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BLP3K28S" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BLP3K28S?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">512GB 版本</a>售价加 70 美元。 S23+ 是 Galaxy S23 和 S23 Ultra 之间的中间产品。它具有与前者相同的处理器、三摄像头系统和 1080p 分辨率，但它提供了更大的 6.6 英寸 OLED 显示屏，而没有增加后者的重量。它还支持比 S23 更快的充电速度，最大功率为 45W，而不是 25W。副编辑 Cherlynn Low 在今年 2 月份的评测中给 Galaxy S23+ 打出了<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-s23-review-a-solid-phone-thats-probably-not-worth-the-upgrade-173026346.html">86 分的分数</a>。</p><h2>谷歌 Pixel 7 Pro </h2><p><core-commerce id="da5ff31ee4c3413fa5303cfc2b8c3f38" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>谷歌的三款 Pixel 7 手机也在 Prime Day 期间打折。首先， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJDUVdZUjJaP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFwaC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNzk4MjUwYTYtZTNmOS00OWU4LTkzYzYtYjhhZGQ4YzY0MWVhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAQvOVe30gw8g-n0mzL7URK07hZQsyVBCSTX4lC74PM1P&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BCQWYR2Z" class="rapid-with-clickid">Pixel 7 Pro</a> 128GB 型号降至 649 美元， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJDUVZGUUhEP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFwaC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNzk4MjUwYTYtZTNmOS00OWU4LTkzYzYtYjhhZGQ4YzY0MWVhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAQonsCBMGQp0xGTyf1gvmcBkzg20m3ABo05iGXhMvb2K&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BCQVFQHD" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BCQVFQHD?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">256GB 型号</a>降至 749 美元， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJDUVY0WUNHP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFwaC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNzk4MjUwYTYtZTNmOS00OWU4LTkzYzYtYjhhZGQ4YzY0MWVhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAafcTjtAumhMmOq2QyyyAF3lxDmeU4YIghSeXPC3E47U&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BCQV4YCG" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BCQV4YCG?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">512GB 型号</a>降至 849 美元。每款产品均比 Google 标价低 250 美元，比我们之前看到的最低价低 50 美元。</p><p>在我们的<a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-smartphones-140004900.html">智能手机购买指南</a>中，我们将 Pixel 7 Pro 称为最好的“拍照手机”，因为与 Galaxy S23 Ultra 等替代产品相比，它能拍摄出始终清晰、准确的照片，而且更省事。它在弱光环境下的表现也优于同类产品。谷歌对 Android 的采用总体上比三星的 One UI 更干净，Pixel 7 和 Pixel 7 Pro 都将在 2027 年底之前收到<a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://support.google.com/pixelphone/answer/4457705?hl=en#zippy=%2Cpixel-later">安全更新</a>。也就是说，S23 Ultra 的原始性能对于游戏等更复杂的任务来说仍然更好，并且超过了谷歌在显示质量和电池寿命方面的旗舰产品。还值得注意的是，谷歌<a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/pixel-8-pro/">几乎肯定</a>会在今年晚些时候推出新款 Pixel 8 手机。但如果相机质量是您最关心的问题，那么这仍然很有价值。去年秋天，资深作家 Sam Rutherford 给 Pixel 7 Pro <a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-pixel-7-and-pixel-7-pro-review-still-the-best-bargain-in-flagship-phones-170031940.html">的评分为 92 分</a>。</p><h2>谷歌像素 7 </h2><p><core-commerce id="601fa1a06e5c47c3bc623d49ce3ed5a9" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>未锁频版<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:22;pos:1" href="https