9</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 798250a6-e3f9-49e8-93c6-b8add8c641ea</guid><dc:creator>杰夫·邓恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jul 2023 14:30:39 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689171108</ingested><modified> 2023-07-12T14:12:04+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Shopping]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jeff Dunn]]></category><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/a74b8640-20b8-11ee-adbf-018adbe42d3b" width="1621"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/a74b8640-20b8-11ee-adbf-018adbe42d3b" width="1621"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Photo by Cherlynn Low / Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The best Amazon Prime Day phone deals for 2023]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[The best Amazon Prime Day phone deals for 2023]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[WhatsApp will keep your phone number completely private in community chats]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在 WhatsApp 社区中，您的电话号码通常是保密的，但如果您对消息做出反应，您仍有可能会泄露该号码。值得庆幸的是，这可能不会持续太久，因为<em>WABetaInfo</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://wabetainfo.com/whatsapp-is-rolling-out-a-phone-number-privacy-feature-for-communities/">发现</a>WhatsApp 正在更广泛地测试 Beta 用户的“电话号码隐私”功能。启用它后，您的数字将仅对社区管理员和将您保存为联系人的人可见。</p><p>该选项已经进行了几个月的有限测试，但似乎正在向安装了最新 Android 和 iOS 更新的测试版用户广泛推出。我们已向 WhatsApp 母公司 Meta 询问更多细节，但<em>WABetaInfo</em>表示，升级应该会在未来几天惠及更多用户和群体。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>在某些情况下，这一添加可能对隐私至关重要。这使您可以充分参与社区公告组，而不必担心会泄露您的电话号码。除非您接受共享联系信息的请求，否则小人和潜在的欺诈者无法给您打电话或发短信。反过来，这可以帮助您从一开始就放心地使用社区。</p><p>最近几周，WhatsApp 增加了许多隐私功能，包括<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/whatsapps-new-privacy-feature-locks-sensitive-chats-and-hides-them-from-notifications-181005512.html">锁定聊天</a>、自动<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/whatsapp-can-now-automatically-silence-unknown-callers-082512152.html">静音未知来电者</a>以及设置审核。电话号码隐私与该策略一致——这是防止无意中与他人共享敏感数据的另一种保护措施。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/whatsapp-will-keep-your-phone-number-completely-private-in-community-chats-141536708.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/whatsapp-will-keep-your-phone-number-completely-private-in-community-chats-141536708.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 1b4e9511-90cc-451c-a80c-0532d021829a</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jul 2023 14:15:36 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689171043</ingested><modified> 2023-07-12T14:10:46+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="3334" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/3ad713c0-20b4-11ee-bdff-de6f16b6493a" width="5000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3334" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/3ad713c0-20b4-11ee-bdff-de6f16b6493a" width="5000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[SOPA Images via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[BRAZIL - 2023/05/21: In this photo illustration, the WhatsApp logo is displayed on a smartphone screen. (Photo Illustration by Rafael Henrique/SOPA Images/LightRocket via Getty Images)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[In this photo illustration, the WhatsApp logo is displayed...]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Amazon Prime Day 2023 Day 2: The best deals you can still get]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day/">亚马逊 Prime Day</a>的下半场已经到来，你仍然可以买到一堆打折的科技产品。今年，我们对一些我们最喜欢的技术带来了许多可靠的、Prime 独家优惠，包括 Apple AirPods、Google Pixel 手机，当然还有亚马逊自己的设备，如 Echos、Kindle、Fire TV Sticks 等。无论您只是想抽出时间来购买亚马逊 Prime Day 优惠，还是今天返回看看还能买到什么折扣商品，我们都在这里收集了最佳 Prime Day 优惠，因此您无需再去寻找他们。</p><h2>苹果AirPods Pro </h2><p><core-commerce id="5af865640a3c4e29b36cbb7dfbb8a785" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>苹果第二代<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQ2WovotMPr9yLYPVXwyANrljUHhEBa9DUXBKVoaTIXT&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-Generation-Cancelling-Transparency-Perso