ommerce id="6570bd26ae35415dad5da6f5f278b691" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>配备 Core i7-12800H 处理器、GeForce RTX 3070 Ti GPU、240Hz QHD 显示屏、16GB RAM 和 1TB SSD <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:84;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlSQkpDOFk5P3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTEzNi0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYWFkZDA1OTYtMTYwYi00ZWUyLWIyMDQtODEzNmFhYjljZTYzIn0&amp;signature=AQAAATr4O2osuxJ6DjJPxooN1U2saEQP4LkwEbrUKzB18tpg&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09RBJC8Y9" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09RBJC8Y9?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">的 Razer Blade 15</a>配置在 Prime Day 降至 1,923 美元。这比近几个月的正常市场价格低了约 375 美元。去年我们给 Blade 15 <a data-i13n="cpos:85;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/razer-blade-15-2022-review-a-real-treat-if-youve-got-the-cash-160032467.html">的评分为 86 分</a>，目前我们在<a data-i13n="cpos:86;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-gaming-laptops-172033838.html">最佳游戏笔记本电脑</a>指南中将其作为首选推荐。此配置是 2022 年型号 - <a data-i13n="cpos:87;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/razer-updates-the-blade-15-with-13th-gen-intel-cpus-and-rtx-40-series-graphics-190544878.html">最新版本</a>主要是规格提升 - 但它仍然足够强大，可以在高设置和帧速率下玩大多数现代游戏，尤其是使用 DLSS 时。不过，为任何刀片笔记本电脑支付高价的主要原因是因为它采用纤薄且具有优质感觉的铝制设计来提供强大的功能。请注意，它可能会很热，并且电池寿命相当短。</p><p><strong><em>您的 Prime 会员日购物指南</em></strong><em>：查看我们所有的</em><a data-i13n="cpos:88;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/topics/prime-day/"><em>Prime 会员日</em></a><em>报道。</em><em>在雅虎生活上</em><em>购买</em><a data-i13n="cpos:89;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/lifestyle/prime-day-2023-191047652.html"><em>最优惠的 Prime Day 优惠</em></a>。<em>关注 Engadget，了解</em><a data-i13n="cpos:90;pos:1" href="http